## Firebase secrets — the SERVICE ACCOUNT JSON is sensitive (server-level
## access). Client-side configs (firebase_options.dart, google-services.json,
## GoogleService-Info.plist) are safe to commit — those keys are embedded in
## every published build of the app anyway; security comes from Firestore rules.
firebase-key.json
*-service-account.json
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json

